1774
01:47:17.208 --> 01:47:19.625
Come on. Let’s go out on the balcony.
it’s beautiful outside.

1775
01:47:19.708 --> 01:47:21.083
- You’ll see.
- Come on.

1776
01:47:21.166 --> 01:47:22.500
- Move your ass!
- Ouch!

1777
